Class GameStatistic.AIStatistic

java.lang.Object
model.GameStatistic.AIStatistic
Enclosing class:
GameStatistic
public static class GameStatistic.AIStatistic extends Object
The AIStatistic class is responsible for tracking and displaying statistics for a single AI. It tracks metrics.
